From 192.168.227.2 icmp_seq=1 Destination Net Unreachable
Server:		192.168.227.2
Address:	192.168.227.2#53

Non-authoritative answer:
l8u8ahkz3cr2djkwxva0fibcr3x0lt9oxgk68v.oastify.com	canonical name = PublicInteractionNLB-3bddf5ff6abb91b6.elb.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com.

Authoritative answers can be found from:

From 192.168.227.2 icmp_seq=2 Destination Net Unreachable
From 192.168.227.2 icmp_seq=3 Destination Net Unreachable
From 192.168.227.2 icmp_seq=4 Destination Net Unreachable

--- 1 ping statistics ---
4 packets transmitted, 0 received, +4 errors, 100% packet loss, time 3007ms
